&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Key Themes and Ideas from Interview with Jeff Bezos @ Amazon, at Dealbook Event 2024 
    &lt;div id=&#34;key-themes-and-ideas-from-interview-with-jeff-bezos--amazon-at-dealbook-event-2024&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
